BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[FFXIV] Play Free for up to 4 Days in the Latest Free Login Campai
 gn!
DTSTART:20260515T083000Z
DTEND:20260529T083000Z
DTSTAMP:20260519T095238Z
UID:e1c7eb7103a7@mmo-calendar
DESCRIPTION:In the hope that would-be adventurers can experience all that 
 FFXIV has to offer\, we are pleased to announce the latest Free Login Camp
 aign.\n\n\n\nFollow the Trail to the Heavens! In Patch 7.5\, you can face 
 Enuo in the Unmaking\, take a stroll through Windurst: The Third Walk in t
 he FINAL FANTASY XI alliance raid crossover\, and leap into battle in Arch
 eia Harmonias\, an all-new arena for Crystalline Conflict.\n\nA host of ot
 her additions and adjustments will make your time in Eorzea more streamlin
 ed and enjoyable\, including increased furnishing placement limits\, the c
 onsolidation of dyes\, and additional pieces of gear that can now be conve
 rted to outfit glamour or stored in the armoire.\n\n With the introduction
  of Patch 7.5\, the Shadowbringers expansion can now be played as part of 
 the FINAL FANTASY XIV Starter Edition. The expansion will be automatically
  registered to your account if you already own the Starter Edition\, so wh
 y not take this opportunity to jump into the adventure?
URL:https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/topics/detail/9abe0a9087a62bb
 c886fa2fbd189379445092a97
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[FFXIV] The Maiden's Rhapsody Returns May 8!
DTSTART:20260501T080100Z
DTEND:20260515T080100Z
DTSTAMP:20260519T095240Z
UID:f71762420924@mmo-calendar
DESCRIPTION:Experience the intriguing tale bridging Hydaelyn and Vana'diel
  as The Maiden's Rhapsody─a past collaboration with FFXI─returns to th
 e realm once more! Embark on a journey with one of Vana'diel's heroes and 
 discover what twists of fate brought her to our realm.
URL:https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/topics/detail/2e44e0fa9b12c05
 7ed8ab12b5af966c452eeddd9
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[FFXIV] PvP Series 10 Draws to a Close as Series 11 Begins!
DTSTART:20260428T093200Z
DTEND:20260512T093200Z
DTSTAMP:20260519T095242Z
UID:69565ae2a051@mmo-calendar
DESCRIPTION:After myriad battles fought and won\, PvP Series 10 has ended.
  Rewards for Series 10 may be claimed until the end of Series 11.\n\nFor t
 hose eager to dive back into the fray\, we are pleased to announce that Pv
 P Series 11 has officially begun! The more you play\, the more bountiful t
 he rewards\, so we encourage all players to try their hand at PvP!\n\nRead
  on for details.
URL:https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/topics/detail/3eff5caeb29649b
 c49281e45cb4f301be2ccfc23
END:VEVENT
